1 A BILL ENTITLED
2 AN ACT concerning
3 Real Property – Residential Lease – Terminology
4 FOR the purpose of replacing the term “landlord” with “rental property owner” and “tenant”
5 with “resident” in the context of residential leases; and generally relating to the
6 terminology for residential leases.
