12 [(4) “Tenant” means a tenant or a prospective tenant.]
13 (b) (1) A [landlord] RENTAL PROPERTY OWNER may not impose a security
14 deposit in excess of the equivalent of two months’ rent per dwelling unit, regardless of the
15 number of [tenants] RESIDENTS.
